    <h1>FIRST YEAR AT DUKE</h1>
    <h4>Transitioning and Succeeding</h4>
    <p>Most students navigate all of the new experiences of their first year at Duke without significant problems. It is also not uncommon for many students to find the transition to college more challenging than they expected. Even those that do struggle, initially, usually end up adjusting in their first year and enjoy success at Duke.</p>
